event.title: Open-source party with the Israel OS community
event.metaTitle: Open-source party with the Israel OS community
event.metaDesc: Open-source parties are part of our OS community tradition. Everyone comes up and introduces themselves in the context of open-source. Working together to figure out how each one can proceed and how to make connections with each participant.
event.content:
Open-source parties are part of our OS community tradition.

Everyone comes up and introduces themselves in the context of open-source.

Working together to figure out how each one can proceed and how to make connections with each participant.
